Scoop rainbow sherbet into a bowl; allow to sit at room temperature until it turns slushy.. Mix black cherry-flavored drink mix with sugar and water in a pitcher; stir until sugar is dissolved. Add orange-flavored drink mix; stir well. Pour into a punch bowl. Top with pineapple soda; stir well. Stir the rainbow sherbet with a wooden spoon until it turns a grayish color. Scoop into the punch bowl. Stir slowly to break up the sherbet.